---
title: Carb Smart Tofu Bulgur Bowls with DIY Jalapeño-Ranch Dressing
description: Jalapeño-ranch dressing steals the show in this quick and well-balanced bowl. Smoky baked tofu pairs perfectly with creamy ranch, while lemony bulgur brings pops of brightness to every bite!

